<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Verification Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #5850ec;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .verification-code {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: #5850ec;
    }
    .note {
      background-color: #f7fafc;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border-left: 4px solid #5850ec;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">Music Community</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <h2>Complete Your Registration</h2>
    
    <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
    
    <p>Thanks for signing up for Music Community! To complete your registration, please use the verification code below:</p>
    
    <div class="verification-code">{{code}}</div>
    
    <p>Enter this code on the verification page to activate your account.</p>
    
    <div class="note">
      <p>This code will expire in 1 hour for security reasons.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>If you didn't create an account on Music Community, please ignore this email.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Music Community Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Music Community. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://musiccommunity.example.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
      <a href="https://musiccommunity.example.com/terms">Terms of Service</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
